de.adorsys.datasafe.metainfo.version.impl.version.latest.actions

Class LatestReadImpl<V extends LatestDFSVersion>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.adorsys.datasafe.metainfo.version.impl.version.latest.actions.LatestReadImpl<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - version tag
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    VersionedRead<V>, WithVersionStrategy<V>, ReadFromPrivate

    public class LatestReadImpl<V extends LatestDFSVersion>
extends Object
implements VersionedRead<V>
    Default versioned resource reader that resolves latest resource link location using EncryptedLatestLinkService, follows that link by reading its content to get latest blob location, reads and decrypts latest blob content using ReadFromPrivate
